  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study evaluates the efficacy and tolerability of a risk- and subtype-adapted chemotherapy
      over one year, followed by randomized either intensified or conventional maintenance therapy.
      It includes a distinct protocol for the subgroup 'mature B-ALL',
    </textblock>
